These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Cigar: pall-mall, cain, oliveros
1. Cigar:cain is on the right of Cigar:oliveros##1
2. Cigar:pall-mall is on the far right##1
3. Cigar:pall-mall is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Cigar   | oliveros | cain | pall-mall |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: coffee, cola, hot-chocolate
1. Beverage:cola is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:coffee is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Beverage   | coffee | hot-chocolate | cola |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Game: monopoly, poker, whist
1. Game:poker is in an even position##4
2. Game:poker is on the left or right of Game:whist##3
3. Game:whist is on the right of Game:poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Game   | monopoly | poker | whist |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
Pet: ferret, frog, rat
1. Pet:frog is in an odd position##4
2. Pet:rat is on the left of Pet:frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Pet   | ferret | rat | frog |

